Woman: AND THEY CERTAINLY TOOK
 ADVANTAGE OF EVERY MOMENT THAT
 WHEN WE WERE WITH THE BABY,

00:03:54.000 --> 00:03:57.000
TO EITHER DESTROY THE HOUSE
OR TO HURT EACH OTHER

00:03:57.000 --> 00:03:59.000
OR FIGHT
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

