Woman: TWO DIFFERENT TEACHERS
 HAVE SAID THAT SHE'S LIKE

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.000
GONNA A WOMAN OF THE NINETIES
 OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT,

00:04:08.000 --> 00:04:12.000
WHICH I THOUGHT WAS
SO FUNNY AT FOUR YEARS OLD,
BUT SHE GIVES THAT IMPRESSION.

00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:15.000
WHERE ERIKA,
AS THE MIDDLE CHILD,

00:04:15.000 --> 00:04:19.000
SHE'S EXTREMELY INTELLIGENT
 AND SHE THINKS.

