MY DAUGHTER, SHE'S GONNA BE
 ONE OF THOSE STUDENTS

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:23.000
THAT MAY SIT IN CLASS,
 ALWAYS KNOW THE ANSWER,

00:04:23.000 --> 00:04:27.000
BUT MAY NEVER RAISE HER HAND
 AND GIVE IT OUT.

00:04:27.000 --> 00:04:30.000
HER HUMOR IS, UH,
 IT'S MORE OFF THE CUFF,

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:33.000
AND HANNAH'S JUST RIGHT NOW
IN HER OWN WHATEVER--

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:36.000
A BUG FLYING BY JUST
CRACKS HER UP, OR WHATEVER.

00:04:36.000 --> 00:04:40.000
SO, I MEAN, THAT'S JUST
THE CUTENESS OF BEING
A TWO-YEAR-OLD.

00:04:40.000 --> 00:04:42.000
OF COURSE YOU HAVE TO HAVE
A HIGH TOLERANCE LEVEL

00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:44.000
WHEN YOU HAVE
 THREE YOUNG BOYS.

00:04:44.000 --> 00:04:47.000
RIGHT HERE?
WHAT DID EVAN DO?

