AND I'D ALWAYS BE
 RIGHT THERE LIKE,
 "OKAY, OKAY, LET'S STOP."

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:12.000
I THINK ONCE HANNAH CAME ALONG,
 I PROBABLY DIDN'T HAVE
 THE TIME TO DO THAT,

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:16.000
AND SO THEY HAVE LEARNED TO
WORK THINGS OUT ON THEIR OWN.

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.000
AND NOW I'LL EVEN
SAY TO THEM,

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:20.000
IF ONE OF THEM COMES
 RUNNING TO ME WITH,

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:24.000
"SHE DID THIS,
 SHE DID THAT," AND, UM--

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:26.000
MY RESPONSE NOW,
INSTEAD OF YELLING,

00:05:26.000 --> 00:05:30.000
IS TO JUST SAY,
"LET'S TRY TO WORK IT OUT."

