SOME CHALLENGES

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:46.000
THAT A FIRST-BORN WILL FACE.

00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:49.000
THE FIRST-BORN CHILD IS OFTEN
PRESSURED VERY HIGHLY

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:53.000
BY HIS PARENTS TO SUCCEED,
BECAUSE THE PARENTS WANT TO FEEL

00:10:53.000 --> 00:10:55.000
THAT THEY'RE VERY GOOD
AT THEIR JOB,

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:57.000
AND THAT THEIR CHILD
WILL HAVE A GOOD LIFE.

00:10:57.000 --> 00:11:01.000
AND SO THE FIRST-BORN CHILD MAY
END UP BEING VERY SUCCESSFUL,

00:11:01.000 --> 00:11:03.000
BUT MAY END UP BEING
VERY HARD ON HIMSELF.

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:06.000
- A PERFECTIONIST.
- YES.

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.000
- IT'S NOT EASY.
- NO.

00:11:07.000 --> 00:11:09.000
AND THE SECOND CHILD OFTEN

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:12.000
IS A LITTLE BIT
 MORE EASY-GOING,

00:11:12.000 --> 00:11:15.000
WHY, BECAUSE THE PARENTS
ARE VERY MUCH MORE EDUCATED,

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:17.000
THEY UNDERSTAND
WHAT CHILDREN ARE LIKE,

00:11:17.000 --> 00:11:19.000
THEY'RE CALMER,
AND SO THEY...

00:11:19.000 --> 00:11:21.000
THEY ALSO HAVE
LESS TIME TO FOCUS

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:24.000
AND SCRUTINIZE
THEIR SECOND CHILD.

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:26.000
SO THE SECOND CHILD
 CAN GO OUT INTO LIFE

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.000
FEELING MUCH MORE RELAXED.

00:11:28.000 --> 00:11:32.000
HOWEVER, THE SECOND CHILD
OFTEN FEELS VERY INADEQUATE

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:34.000
BECAUSE HE LOOKS AT
HIS OLDER SISTER

00:11:34.000 --> 00:11:36.000
