"WHAT'S WRONG WITH ME?

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:43.000
THERE'S SOMETHING WRONG.
MAYBE I'M NOT AS GOOD."

00:11:43.000 --> 00:11:46.000
A SECOND CHILD MIGHT BE
VERY HIGHLY COMPETITIVE.

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:48.000
