- AND SUCCESSFUL, YES.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:54.000
'CAUSE THEY'VE FOUND
THE ROLE FOR THEMSELVES

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:56.000
THAT'S DIFFERENT
FROM THE OLDER ONE?

00:11:56.000 --> 00:11:59.000
