MIGHT BECOME VERY INTIMIDATED

00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:07.000
AND DECIDE "I CAN'T BE AS GOOD,
SO I MAY AS WELL NOT TRY."

00:12:07.000 --> 00:12:09.000
