FOR PARENTS

00:12:09.000 --> 00:12:11.000
TO EXPLAIN TO THE SECOND CHILD
IT'S AN AGE DIFFERENCE.

00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:13.000
THERE'S NOTHING
WRONG WITH YOU,

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:15.000
YOU'RE JUST AS GOOD
AS YOUR OLDER BROTHER,

00:12:15.000 --> 00:12:17.000
AND THEN THERE ARE OTHER STEPS
 YOU NEED TO TAKE AS WELL.

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:20.000
YOU NEED TO ENCOURAGE
 THE SECOND-BORN CHILD

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:22.000
TO TRY THINGS
THAT HE'S INTERESTED IN,

00:12:22.000 --> 00:12:25.000
THAT HE'S SUCCESSFUL AT,
PRAISE THE YOUNGER CHILD.

00:12:25.000 --> 00:12:28.000
PICK OUT SOMETHING
ABOUT HIM THAT STANDS OUT.

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:29.000
YES.

00:12:30.000 --> 00:12:33.000
AND THAT WILL GIVE HIM
A GREAT DEAL OF CONFIDENCE.

00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.000
