THE PARENTS ARE SO BUSY

00:13:03.000 --> 00:13:05.000
THEY'RE NOT GIVING
THE YOUNGER SIBLING

00:13:05.000 --> 00:13:09.000
THAT EXTRA TIME AND ATTENTION,
THAT EXTRA STIMULATION.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.000
AND IF A CHILD
FELT COMPETENT

00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:13.000
ABOUT WHAT THEY
WERE TRYING TO DO

00:13:13.000 --> 00:13:16.000
AND COULD BE RESPECTED
FOR THEIR INDIVIDUALITY,

00:13:16.000 --> 00:13:19.000
THAT WOULD GIVE A CHILD BACK
AN UNDERSTANDING OF THEMSELVES

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:21.000
AND ALSO THE MOTIVE

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:24.000
TO DEAL WITH FINDING
A ROLE IN THE FAMILY,

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.000
AND THEN
FEELING GOOD ABOUT IT,

00:13:26.000 --> 00:13:28.000
AND THEN BEING READY
TO FIND A ROLE IN,

00:13:28.000 --> 00:13:31.000
