00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:34.000
IF YOU GIVE A CHILD
THE FEELING YOU'RE LOVED

00:13:34.000 --> 00:13:36.000
AND YOU'RE SPECIAL TO US,

00:13:37.000 --> 00:13:39.000
THEN YOU WILL CUT DOWN
ON THE KIND OF RIVALRY

00:13:39.000 --> 00:13:41.000
WE SEE IN FAMILIES.

00:13:41.000 --> 00:13:43.000
I THINK THERE'S A NORMAL
AMOUNT OF RIVALRY,

00:13:43.000 --> 00:13:46.000
BUT IF YOU GIVE CHILDREN
THAT FEELING OF CONFIDENCE

00:13:46.000 --> 00:13:48.000
THEN THAT WILL HAPPEN LESS.

00:13:48.000 --> 00:13:50.000
AND SO IN A WAY,
WHAT YOU'VE EXPLAINED TO ME

00:13:51.000 --> 00:13:53.000
